 Supporting Material/References (Screenshots)\n {F400895}\n{F400896}\n\n## Impact\n\n* XSS but can not bypass CSP\n* inject html code","bounty_amount":"500.0","formatted_bounty":"$500","weakness":{"id":63,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - DOM"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":400895,"file_name":"dom_xss_h1.JPG","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/400/895/25206fb7e11126f94db68ed8158fcc1140205597/dom_xss_h1.JPG?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22dom_xss_h1.JPG%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27dom_xss_h1.JPG\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fjpeg\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQXIKJZ7C2%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T093719Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECkaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIB%2BrDxbmS4wVxSKaoLhBChaC%2FbLWvZOww6wyLYbJvocEAiEAsSYVfAsOKBfCVLWqx8pZmM%2Fla32D3gkpkjdHA2cePVEquwUI8v%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDG8g5yTABXLIBNO5xSqPBT7Z%2F%2BYv2A6mpBiAO0aYEVqhWnAtBVqc%2F3wFCHNv4v5Rj1PMZtz3O5Rlw8y7kdaoE9PKQhcb0LmTaBk7ql%2BnDvtyQWuvBAIkTamcXqYiFz4vs6ktUTiNHKJPnLAld8ZvDi7lCqePHofLUD26xlbedqVmwnagBykUN5%2FfZ8pLRtMEhjXlueBbzZYfwTd%2BWVdKpokTEsCBZsh3wN2wYt5U6x%2BCRh%2F9H3o1rDBiAPDS%2BsZunjbwwkoBSqJWkCOaVFvNqYQ0BJWfWpI4PH37v1hynKFiQpETckWcdczntt5jQej1wavvwql%2FihQOdXP83Lid5y3GR9hNH5wVckrqRZXM%2BKNAhNdBZEfGdyqbEV9E3NvEt1s2YEwreXvqrYODBOGiawLOU2ykwDqpjgCySVIVatR2uwTfby3Oy9w834OhUXmx5H3hKGEBPW%2BHOyHBbgtUiUPBLXi2ut75AkPC0jnEP5cZk3LBQvjc3JoEtABcu27pmcoD9yorGpZnJfiwsvtB2iBDCIb91RXeYXfMeKtFboYFi6n571ALR728FDl%2BFs805kZXrzOzsfni5ivp%2FbWSGMscE85%2Bs7UnBqJRY2hXy%2FLgyAviaqEwy6aAlgZB02dxEnpunLpU1ubY1asbJ2NArDaRLeLMqILEtNkDAhkn2YIyRKf4E8ZGm72aGyHHcNQgYIofYcil7vEDm6T2Nyr9k3O3chwGN82D4WdIET9hSjnslmfp%2FN14M9vQgu5dqwpuuAdoLAgvhkR1q0y584seA%2BXWDdyT3giEY1DsGatq3Lvdb0cgdXWwdR4Eijk0RUjb8j6GlbPX%2Brc4A15mRmEgn65ihkBt1A%2BcXPhZJk1vS